reviewText: slednecks need to get their films back up to par, this one sucks compared to 509 volume 8 , save your money and purchase 509 dvd you will love it.  sled necks even made my 11 year old boy bored, watched it once and we are giving it away, 509 we are keeping to watch over and over again...
Blue ray has great picture quality and slednecks features great riders but I didn't think the content was the best out of all the slednecks series so far
